    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1288">
<l>iḷittakka viṉṉā ceyiṉuṅ kaḷittārkkuk</l>
<l>kaḷḷaṟṟē kaḷvaniṉ mārpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O you rogue! your breast is to me what liquor is to those who rejoice in it, though it only gives them an unpleasant disgrace.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
